Name: Hell Runner
About the game: Hell Runner is a fast Paced first person platformer game where you try to beat each level as fast as possible. Current early access have 2 chapter and 18 level to play and more is on the way. Go through eight chapters to deliver the necklace to its rightful owner. Go through each level and try to beat it fast as you can. Chapters Eight chapters: Hell, Underground, Spring, Summer, Fall, Winter, Sky, Heaven. Each Chapter gonna have nine levels for you to beat. TRAIN YOURSELF Try to achieve the faster time possible for each level and beat others for the top ten Highscore. . Update 0.3.X Chapter 3: Spring Chapter. New Ability: Dash. Update 0.4.X Chapter 4: Summer Chapter. New Ability Double Jump. Update 0.5.X Chapter 5: Fall Chapter. New Ability: Telekinesis Update 0.6.X Chapter 6: Winter Chapter. New Mechanic: Rails to Glide Update 0.7.X Chapter 7: Sky Chapter. New Ability: Fly Update 0.8.X Final Chapter 8: Heaven Chapter. Update 0.9.X Hub Level  Removal of level select panel. Global Score System Release 1.0.0 Multiplayer Game Mod Multiplayer levels to race with people that have interactive traps.  Hub level also become a lobby to show off your customized home/room to others or chill with them. Character customization. Hub customization. Global Chat System on Hub
